{"tid":1980600,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"（房屋達人請入）有層樓揸手想換樓或投資","createTime":"2020-04-20T07:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T14:56:40.000Z","uid":117834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"61934b98f9fd8327cfdb1fd7aab9f92f7be13f8f","tid":1980600,"uid":117834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:43:40.000Z","msg":"4x年樓齡 銀行估價670萬 近地鐵站 最近兩個月前成交640萬 <br />\n<br />\n490呎想換三房 諗緊oma oma 607呎 8球 每個月供12000蚊左右 （三個人分 非高收入人士） <br />\n<br />\n或者<br />\n<br />\n換村屋地下連有入車花園（5 6球可能都有靚盤非太偏癖） 無咁大經濟負擔 可能借少少裝修 每個月還一兩千<br />\n<br />\n想問下會唔會有其他投資選擇<br />\n<br />\n按住現住層樓再放租供樓 去比首期oma oma自住等兩三年理想會升 <br />\n<br />\n希望有投資達人可以比下意見 小弟暫時一知半解 家母嫌現住樓太殘要裝修或換樓"},{"pid":"ea4583c6df3a8c02965f5c3794b57a98b3e53d5d","tid":1980600,"uid":117834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:48:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f837194bf726b6aa7d7c2bc8a1cd474b5c04262","tid":1980600,"uid":9387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:51:55.000Z","msg":"三個人月入夠做兩層樓按揭?"},{"pid":"d9b0d1a1e9b9915b7a10637244da773f152e11b0","tid":1980600,"uid":176760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:56:42.000Z","msg":"人工幾多先？ 你有按揭係手再過多次壓力測試要求唔同咖喎"},{"pid":"0bb61b7b81dcc764f4ba97ef5c4f2da2506c7177","tid":1980600,"uid":117834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9b0d1a1e9b9915b7a10637244da773f152e11b0","tid":1980600,"uid":176760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:56:42.000Z","msg":"人工幾多先？ 你有按揭係手再過多次壓力測試要求唔同咖喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T08:07:18.000Z","msg":"加埋50k左右 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b89ab5e0709e0d058b91b542db7c28a1e121ea6","tid":19